  -- The total imbalance of a factorization f is the sum over primes p ≤ L of |v_p(m)| for m in a
  -- The cardinality of a factorization f is the cardinality of the multiset a
  -- The total score of a factorization f is the sum over primes p ≤ L of (L+1 - v_p(m)) for m in a
